{"tid":1489620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（細思極恐) 林鄭肯撤回方案 難保他日秋後算帳","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T09:56:30.000Z","uid":160887,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"76546788102753328dd10c8cdc4b5f497931023c","tid":1489620,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"呢個政府已經冇誠信可言<br />\n就算佢肯滿足我地五大訴求其中幾項<br />\n<br />\n肯撤回，肯放人咁又點<br />\n過一排在捉返嚟班人入去仲得<br />\n<br />\n而家中央出到聲要九月前擺平香港嘅風波<br />\n林鄭亦都有可能作出讓步，影響到中立嘅市民<br />\n<br />\n港獨係好明顯違反咗一國兩制<br />\n但邊撚個相俾你個垃圾國家統治<br />\n<br />\n如果你班香港人仲唔醒覺，仲唔肯出嚟<br />\n下一個俾人清算嘅，唔係達哥，而係你哋每一個人"},{"pid":"0c603857e16820b3c813329e7cdf01ba98f5de18","tid":1489620,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ee72342b0f3ca2103031cb4384a580bc57c3c5","tid":1489620,"uid":215876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"你可以放心<br />\n佢一個五大訴求都無應過"},{"pid":"6a100210430bdf6ad32890ecabb9834fb39f4180","tid":1489620,"uid":293698,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52b8fa2ce0385e01c019997bd73846e23ea8a06a","tid":1489620,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ee72342b0f3ca2103031cb4384a580bc57c3c5","tid":1489620,"uid":215876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"你可以放心<br />\n佢一個五大訴求都無應過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"中央落得order就要做嘢㗎啦"},{"pid":"c97ff0dc3ae1ae76efdbebfd9e8b7f4114871ec7","tid":1489620,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a100210430bdf6ad32890ecabb9834fb39f4180","tid":1489620,"uid":293698,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime